<item>Geary, David C., Byrd-Craven, Jennifer, Hoard, Mary K., Vigil, Jacob, Numtee, Chattavee. 2003. Evolution and development of boys’ social behavior. Developmental Review. 23: 444-470.
      <para id="id1168595054858">This article examines both one-on-one and coalition competition between males from an evolutionary perspective. It then applies this analysis to the social development of young boys, including “rough and tumble play.”</para>
